  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    Datanika's API is designed for autonomous AI agents. Two unauthenticated discovery documents
    tell the agent everything it needs to know, and a 5-tier capability stack lets it build,
    validate, and run pipelines without human intervention.
  </p>

